		</tr></table><hr /><h2>Latest revision as of 11:53, 2 June 2011</h2>
<p>This session discussed a potential approach to building large systems in a way to minimize their complexity.
</p><p>Please get in touch with us - Ben Moseley (benATmoseley.name) and Peter Marks (publicATindigomail.net) if you have any private comments / questions (good, bad or ugly - we don't mind!), or add stuff below for public viewing.
</p>
